      "cookedHtml": "<p>If you manage work across multiple boards in <strong><a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a></strong>, you know how quickly things can get messy.</p>\n<p>That’s exactly why we built <strong><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000876/mirror-item-multiple-boards\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Mirror Item Multiple Boards</a></strong> — to give you powerful, reliable syncing across boards without manual duplication, broken automations, or constant cross-checking.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-246650-what-the-app-helps-you-do-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-246650-what-the-app-helps-you-do-1\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/repeat_button.png?v=15\" title=\":repeat_button:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":repeat_button:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> What the app helps you do</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Mirror items+subitems+updates across multiple boards and keep them in sync<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Add <strong>clickable links to jump to linked items</strong>, and emoji indicators to identify mirrored items at a glance<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Setup automations like ‘<strong>When status changes to something, mirror item to Target Board Target Group</strong>’<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Identify which boards updates(comments) are syncing from<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Save hours of manual updates<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Option to auto-fill connect board columns<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Create a master board with tasks from multiple boards</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/9/4/9400ef6b21cfa296cfd69e3733637254fdb6a443.jpeg\" title=\"15\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/9/4/9400ef6b21cfa296cfd69e3733637254fdb6a443_2_690x345.jpeg\" alt=\"15\" width=\"690\" height=\"345\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">15</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 253 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/b/1b371338040ef67b31bda5f7977093fa72ef0d17.png\" title=\"19\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/1/b/1b371338040ef67b31bda5f7977093fa72ef0d17_2_690x345.png\" alt=\"19\" width=\"690\" height=\"345\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">19</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 210 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/1/c147b5f8a043953baacce5d66a686324ac61cbbb.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/c/1/c147b5f8a043953baacce5d66